<h2>Global Change Acronyms and Abbreviations, Continued</h2>

The table below is a list of global change acronyms and abbreviations
gathered together by the GCRIO from the <a href="OCP/toc.html">FY 
1995</a>, <a href="ocp96/toc.html">FY 1996</a>, and <a 
href="ocp97/toc.html">FY 1997</a> editions of <strong>Our 
Changing
Planet: The U.S. Global Change Research Program</strong>, and
<a href="GCDIS/iplan/tocgcdip.html">The U.S. Global Change Data and
Information System (GCDIS) Implementation Plan</a>.<p>

