<title>Our Changing Planet - Atmospheric Modeling</title>
<body>

<img align=left alt=Model Visualizations src=gifs/pg68earths.gif>

<h2>Atmosphere Model Simulation</h2>

General circulation models provide projections of global changes.  
These reults show surface air temperature anomalies 12 years after 
an instantaneous doubling of CO<sub>2</sub>.  Deep red over most of 
Eurasia and northern North America indicates increases greater than 
5&#176 C.
