<h3><em><center>Priorities for the Human Dimensions of Global Change 
Research Include</h3></em></center>

<ul>
<p><li>Impacts of population growth, migration, and social and 
institutional change on the environment and on international 
environmental negotiations.

<p><li>Processes through which individuals and groups anticipate and 
adapt to global change.

<p><li>Impacts of changing environmental conditions on human health, 
