epidemiology of communicable diseases.

<p><li>Economic issues, including the impacts of environmental 
change on international trade and the development of global models 
for different economic sectors.

<p><li>Governmental and legal dimensions of global change, including 
institutional decision-making processes.

<p><li>Economic and social processes related to the development and 
diffusion of industrial, energy, and environmental technologies.</ul>
