<h1><p align=center>The Probability of Sea Level Rise</h1>
<h4><p align=center>By</h4>
<h3><p align =center>James G. Titus
<br align=center>US Environmental Protection Agency
<p align=center>Vijay K. Narayanan
<br align=center>Rockville, Maryland</h3>

Below are on-line text and downloadable WordPerfect versions of the EPA Report "The Probability of Sea Level Rise".
Both contain the text and tables that were submitted by EPA to its
contractor for editing.  Readers interested in examining
the figures should obtain the hard copy.  Because changes in figure
numbers and in wording were made to Chapters 2-6 in the final
draft, the authors suggest that anyone needing to directly should
obtain the hard copy.  The results chapters (Chapter 7, 8, and 9) and
the summary have not been changed.<p>

        The hard copy of this report can be obtained from the EPA by faxing a
request to 513-489-8695,  or writing to National Center for
Environmental Publications and Information, P.O. Box 42419,
Cincinatti, Ohio, 45242.  Substantive comments and questions
concerning the report should be emailed to the author:
<a href="mailto:Titus.Jim@EPAmail.EPA.GOV">Titus.Jim@epamail.epa.gov</a>
  (202-260-7821).<p>
