<DOCHDR>
http://gcrio.gcrio.org:80/geo/volcanic.html 198.76.82.10 19970101080221 text/html 9669
HTTP/1.0 200 Document follows
Date: Wed, 01 Jan 1997 08:02:29 GMT
Server: NCSA/1.5.2
