Listed below are some of the major regional and international governmental and
non-governmental organizations involved in research, monitoring and/or the
provision of information on two or more geoindicators. Many of these are
affiliated to the International Union of Geological Sciences (IUGS) from which
further information may be available. Others are listed in the checklist under
'Other Sources Of Information', where an indication is also given of national,
regional, municipal departments, agencies and authorities that may also be
helpful.<p>

