<DOCNO>WT24-B15-239</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA001-000008-B031-137</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://gcrio.gcrio.org:80/gwcc/part1.html 198.76.82.10 19970101062935 text/html 7462
HTTP/1.0 200 Document follows
Date: Wed, 01 Jan 1997 06:29:43 GMT
