</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO>WT24-B15-244</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA001-000011-B028-178</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://gcrio.gcrio.org:80/gwcc/pt1footnote4.html 198.76.82.10 19970101083428 text/html 983
HTTP/1.0 200 Document follows
