<h2>FREE ENVIRONMENTAL CODE OF FEDERAL REGULATIONS CD-ROM</h2>
(Current through 1/1/95)<p>

<hr size=2>
 
The U.S. Code of Federal Regulations are public domain material that may
not be copyrighted. The Environmental CFRs (10, 29, 40, 49) available on
CD-ROM which you may obtain AT NO COST. You have to cover our
out-of-pocket cost for production, software engine fee that we pay to IBM
Corporation and the packaging and shipping costs. This comes to a total of
$24.00<p>
 
If you don't have the money, we simply ask you to explain the reasons and
we will still forward a copy as long as supplies last.<p>
 
<b>To obtain your free copy, you must FAX your request to: </b>
<pre>
     SOLUTIONS Software Corporation
     FAX: 407/ 321-3098</pre><p>
 
We will immediately forward your copy along with a request for
reimbursement of our expenses.<p>
 
If you would like to assist us in the free (or at least very minimal cost)
distribution of U.S. Government material, please contact me. We need all
the help we can get.<p>

<blockquote><i>
NOTE: Obviously we don't have an unlimited number of copies available. We
will fulfill requests until our stock is exhausted. 
</i></blockquote><p>

<pre>
Mark Wemhoff
SOLUTIONS Software Corporation
TEL: 407/321-7912</pre>

