<title>Footnote 1 - Model Forum Report</title>
<body>
The increase should not be expected to be uniform in latitude or 
season.  As indicated in point 9, high-latitude precipitation is 
projected to increase.  In mid-latitudes, some models show the 
increase as occurring mostly in the colder half of the year.
