Mexico, 
Biogeography Section IV.8.2 Scale 1:4,000,000. Institute of 
Geography-UNAM 
<br>
<h3>Scenarios</h3>
<p>National Commission for Energy Saving, 1992. Report. CONAE-
SEMIP. Mexico, 
Fed. District. Mexico. Environmental Protection Agency, 1990. 
Report.<br>
